{"tid":466737,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（篤灰）城大涉篤數谷國際排名，最少兩大學舉報","createTime":"2017-11-13T00:02:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-13T08:18:09.000Z","uid":29314,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4f8eb4b724eb038135a9ffe7cd9231f3656a965a","tid":466737,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T00:02:40.000Z","msg":"記者翻查城大向國際高等教育資訊機構QS（Quacquarelli Symonds）提交的學生人數資料，對比本港大學教育資助委員會官方數字，發現兩者差距高達三成。<br />\n<br />\n多名本地大學高層向《蘋果》指控城大涉「報細」學生人數，藉以誇大師生比例力谷排名，據悉，最少兩間本港大學就此向QS投訴。"},{"pid":"6a5a0ed969037f52186bd026aa966b0d3bf4a824","tid":466737,"uid":29314,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T00:03:54.000Z","msg":"多於一名本港大學高層向《蘋果》透露，大學學界早已察覺城大呈報的數據有異，懷疑城大取巧計算全年度「最少人」的日子，例如暑假，「舉例係一個本科新生未入學、畢業生已離校嘅日子，snapshot（定格）咁樣去上報人數，正正等同報少一屆本科生，整體人數差距就差不多係兩、三成」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本報獲悉，最少兩間本地大學曾就此向QS投訴。有熟悉高等教育的學者稱：「我唔知道城大點樣play tricks（玩把戲）、甚至自圓其說，但好明顯嘅係QS顯示嘅資料，根本唔反映城大真實情況。」"},{"pid":"b9aac5bae607730b2c4ca75a2ab195b6c8fedaa5","tid":466737,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T00:04:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171113/large/a0101b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171113%2Flarge%2Fa0101b.gif&h=aef2b9a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7aa801553f9dd33e1cf8ab7cf8ec926a60f6ed0d","tid":466737,"uid":29314,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T00:05:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171113/large/a0101c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171113%2Flarge%2Fa0101c.gif&h=6258b93b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"39e01864a431a0cae0fcc41a78c36a64f16c4abe","tid":466737,"uid":29314,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T00:05:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"htt